y after that. In the same year Ankit won several accolades like FilmFare Award for The Best Music Director, GiMA Awards for The Best Debute in Music & The Best Album of the Year & Zee Cine Awards for The Best Music Director\u2026 \nWith his background in Indian Classical and inspirations like Ricky Martin, A R Rehman, Micheal Jackson to name a few, his work is a fine amalgamation of a very fresh and out of the box mix of the east and the west...\n","birthday":"03\/06\/1990","can_post":false,"category":"Musician\/band","checkins":0,"cover":{"cover_id":780118082095257,"offset_x":0,"offset_y":45,"source":"https:\/\/fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net\/hphotos-ak-xpa1\/t31.0-8\/s720x720\/11078064_780118082095257_1999956981480048232_o.jpg","id":"780118082095257"},"current_location":"Mumbai, Maharashtra, India","has_added_app":false,"hometown":"Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India","is_community_page":false,"is_published":true,"likes":1054884,"link":"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/music.ankit","location":{"city":"Mumbai","country":"India"},"name":"Ankit Tiwari","parking":{"lot":0,"street":0,"valet":0},"talking_about_count":118780,"username":"music.ankit","website":"http:\/\/www.ankittiwari.com","were_here_count":0}